abstract: Yahoo has acquired Inquisitor in a move to improve how search results appear on Apple computers.
lead_paragraph: Yahoo has acquired Inquisitor in a move to improve how search results appear on Apple computers.

headline.main: Yahoo Snaps Up Inquisitor to Help With Apple Searches

abstract: HBO is expected to start selling shows on Apple’s iTunes site, with flexible pricing.
snippet: HBO is expected to start selling shows on Apple’s iTunes site, with flexible pricing.
lead_paragraph: “Time Warner Inc’s HBO cable network is expected to start selling shows on Apple Inc’s iTunes digital entertainment service, with flexible pricing,” Reuters reports.

headline.main: HBO Seen Selling Shows on Apple’s iTunes
